  19 Aug 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> webrat-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Avoid tests depending on launchy which is not in the gentoo tree, bug 430646.

  14 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata.xml so that it's the same as most other packages.

  13 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> webrat-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Use new syntax.

  02 Jul 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> webrat-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Add dependency on mechanize for testing, fixing bug 424387.

  02 Jul 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -webrat-0.7.1.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

*webrat-0.7.3 (22 Apr 2011)

  22 Apr 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +webrat-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  10 Jan 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> webrat-0.7.1.ebuild:
  Keyword ~x86-macos.

  09 Oct 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> webrat-0.7.1.ebuild:
  Depend on rspec-1.

  22 May 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -webrat-0.5.3.ebuild, -webrat-0.6.0.ebuild, -webrat-0.7.0.ebuild:
  Cleanup old versions.

*webrat-0.7.1 (27 Apr 2010)

